{
  "stem": "16163.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a dentist in a different town, in [INAUDIBLE] So my father got himself like a little pass that he could go to [INAUDIBLE] for his teeth.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the way to get out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he told him that in Czechoslovakia, that they emptied out one big town, and it's a ghetto for Jews in the eastern Czechoslovakian area, and also, for a lot of old people from Germany.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he even told my father at that time, if there would be a way of getting me out to try to get me out of Germany.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was too late.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Venkel, Kert Venkel, I believe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Kert Venkel, V-E-N-K-E-L, Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Venkel.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He warned my father, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we saw him again after the war, my mother and I.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we came back, we naturally went to him to see him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they came in with trucks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We know we had-- there was-- physically, of course, physically because we had to get on the trucks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They told us like a day before to get a certain amount of things we could take along, like clothing, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my grandmother was 81 years old at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I never forget the first-- the last thing I-- she said when she stepped out of the house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She said, this is the house where I bore all my children, and now they let me got it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have to leave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, just the-- a matter of fact, what I found out about three, four years ago is that that particular house, the Silverberg house was already in the 1600s registered under the name Silverberg.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the great-great-grandparents must have had it already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it's like forced out of everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
